quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  27,67,"N’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuze bati:- mbega nitwaba twaramaze kuba ivu hamwe n’abavyeyi bacu, niho tuzozurwa"
  27,68,Ntankeka uku niko twemerewe hamwe n’abavyeyi bacu baho hambere bikaba bitari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari inyanduruko z’ububeshi z’abantu bakera
  27,69,"Vuga uti:- nimugende kw’Isi yose hanyuma mwitegereze ukugene vyabaye impera n’imperuka kuri ba bantu babi"
  27,70,"Kandi ntuterwe n’agahinda, kandi ntugire ibibazo kubera ingeso zabo bagira"
  27,71,"Kandi bavuga bati:- iyi ndagano izoboneka ryari nimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  27,72,"Vuga uti:- nkumbure iri hafi yukubashikira kuvyo mwihutira kugira ngo bibe"
  27,73,"Kandi ntankeka Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene imigisha ku bantu bayo, mugabo benshi muribo ntiba shima"
  27,74,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi bw’ivyo munyegeza mubikiriza vyanyu hamwe nivyo muserura
  27,75,"Kandi\tntamabanga\tari\thagati\ty’Amajuru\tn’Isi\tatari\tuko\tari\thagati y’igitabu c’Imana kigaragaza ibintu vyose"
  27,76,Ntankeka iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu irabavuga bene Israeri kubintu vyinshi bijanye nukutumvikana kwabo
  27,77,Mu vy’ukuri iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu n’indongozi n’imigisha ku bantu bayemera
  27,78,"Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe azobacira urubanza rw’amategeko yayo, nayo niyo nyene inguvu n’ubumenyi buhagije"
  27,79,Rero niwizere Imana yawe mu vy’ukuri wewe uri hejuru y’ukuri kuri k’umugaragaro
  27,80,Mu vy’ukuri wewe ntushobora kwumvisha abapfuye ubwo butumwa bwawe canke kwumvisha abatumva mugihe bahindukiye bigira iyo baja
  27,81,"Kandi ntushobora kurongora impumyi ziri mubuzimire bwazo, kandi ntushobora kubumvisha atari abemera amajambo yacu y’Imana, abo rero nibo bagamburutsi"
  27,82,N’imvugo mugihe izoba shikira tuzoba kurira igikoko ngaha kw’Isi kizoba vugisha abo bantu kubera yuko batemera amajambo yacu